725670f-a.text: 82nd Street (left), at the N.E. corner of Roosevelt Avenue, showing the Whelan Drug store occupying the corner site. On Roosevelt Avenue is the elevated station of the I.R.T.-B.M.T. subway. About 1928. Brown Brothers.

725671f.text: 82nd Street, at the N.W. corner of Roosevelt Avenue, showing the new Corn Exchange Bank and adjoining commercial buildings. Note the stairway to the subway elevated station. About 1928. Brown Brothers.
